Product Description

Quilted Jacket

Designed to be both functional and fashionable, this modern travel friendly bomber jacket has a stylish flair. The Ben Martin jacket is reliable, especially as the temperatures drop and a light breeze chills the air. Typically casual, this jacket embodies both retro cool and modern style. It is designed to take you from a party setting to the casual ski mountains in high style.

Read more

Fit and Design

In terms of fit, the cut is ample, so you get generous arm movements and provides warmth and protection without adding bulk. Aesthetically, the design is simple with two large main pockets and a logo on the chest. There is a front zipper, so you can easily open up this jacket.

Lightweight

Other things to look for when choosing a walking jacket are the weight, and what is referred to as packability - how well the jacket folds down. Keeping this in mind, the Ben Martin Quilted Jacket is lightweight and can be easily folded away to fit into a suitcase.

Material

Nylon is strong and elastic. It is also easy to wash and dries rather quickly. It retains its shape rather well after laundering, which ensures longevity of the garment. Nylon fiber is very responsive and resilient as well as relatively resistant to heat, UV rays and chemicals.

Read more

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.
